ric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We\u2019ll start with a few questions about your habits and preferences.\n<\/span><\/span><\/div><div><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br><\/span><\/span><\/div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c4685e47-7fff-5f49-f376-8e0889a537c8\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">How often do you normally drink soft drinks (for example, Coke, Pepsi, soda pop, root beer, etc.)?<\/span><\/span>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"ssb_consumption","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"We\u2019ll start with a few questions about your habits and preferences. How often do you normally dri...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Never"},"2":{"Display":"Once a year"},"3":{"Display":"Once a month"},"4":{"Display":"Once a week"},"5":{"Display":"Once a day"},"6":{"Display":"More than once a day"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID180","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_6fkaYAyCnM3OOge","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID172","SecondaryAttribute":"What is your first name?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"What is your first name?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"firstname","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What is your first 